{[%mdl 8192] B02: Alekhine's Defence: Chase Variation and lines with early Nc3
} 1. e4 Nf6 2. e5 Nd5 3. c4 Nb6 4. d4 (4. a4 d6 (4... a5 5. Ra3 d6 6. exd6 exd6
7. d4 Bf5 8. Re3+ Be7 9. Bd3 Bxd3 10. Qxd3 O-O 11. Rh3 g6 12. b3 Bg5 13. f4
